## Rules

- Backend is organized **feature-first** (`modules/product`, `modules/order`),
  not layer-first. Each module is a vertical slice.
- No `src/` directory inside `server/` вЂ” module/infrastructure/middleware
  folders sit directly under `server/`.
- Only `infrastructure/database/mongodb/` may import `mongoose`.
- Only `infrastructure/payment-gateway/` may import a payment SDK (Razorpay/Stripe).
- Only `infrastructure/storage/` may import a storage SDK (AWS S3, Cloudinary).
- Shared types and validation schemas live **within each app** and are reused
  inside that app:
  - **Client** вЂ” `client/lib/types/` (API shapes, auth types, form schemas)
  - **Server** вЂ” `server/modules/*/*.types.ts`, `*.dto.ts`, and
    `server/shared/` (utils, validation, constants)
  Keep client and server contracts aligned per `17-frontend-integration.mdc`.
